al lifeedit isner started playing tennis seriously at age  he played competitively for westside swim and tennis club in greensboro north carolina throughout his childhood he is a graduate of walter hines page senior high school in greensboro and the university of georgia where he majored in speech communication he currently resides in tampa florida where he trains at the saddlebrook academy alongside other american tennis pros such as james blake and mardy fish isner is a supporter of the fremantle football club in the australian football league and the carolina panthers of the national football league recordsedit these records were attained in the open era of tennis tournament year record accomplished player tied wimbledon   aces in an atp singles match stands alone  aces in a grand slam singles match stands alone  aces in a single set stands alone  games won in a single match stands alone  games lost in a single match that he won stands alone  winners in a single match stands alone longest singles match ever played  hours  minutes nicolas mahut longest play in a single day  hours  minutes nicolas mahut  games in a single day nicolas mahut hall of fame championships  won an atp tournament never facing a break point tommy haas other records   career record in tiebreaks significant finalsedit masters  finalsedit singles  –edit outcome year championship surface opponent score runnerup  indian wells hard roger federer –– – runnerup  cincinnati hard rafael nadal –– –– runnerup  paris masters hard i andy murray – –– – doubles  –edit outcome year championship surface partner opponents score runnerup  rome clay sam querrey bob bryan mike bryan – – winner  rome clay sam querrey mardy fish andy roddick wo runnerup  indian wells hard sam querrey rafael nadal marc lópez – –– winner  shanghai hard jack sock henri kontinen john peers – – atp career finalsedit singles   titles  runnersupedit legend grand slam tournaments – atp world tour finals – atp world tour masters  – atp wor